---
// HockeyGameBot — /support page
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Support HockeyGameBot · Keep the Bots Running</title>
  <meta name="description" content="32 team bots. Live scores. Win probability charts. iOS app. All automated, all season. Help keep HockeyGameBot running.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="HockeyGameBot">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Support HockeyGameBot">
  <meta property="og:description" content="32 team bots. Live scores. Win probability charts. iOS app. All automated, all season. Help keep HockeyGameBot running.">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://hockeygamebot.com/support">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://s3.us-west-000.backblazeb2.com/hockeygamebot-media/hockeygamebot/static/og_image.png">
  <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200">
  <meta property="og:image:height" content="630">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:site" content="@hockeygamebot">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Support HockeyGameBot">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="32 team bots. Live scores. Win probability. iOS app. All automated, all season.">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://s3.us-west-000.backblazeb2.com/hockeygamebot-media/hockeygamebot/static/og_image.png">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Oswald:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOP BAR -->
<div class="topbar">
  <a href="/" class="brand">HGB</a>
  <div class="brand-sub">HockeyGameBot</div>
  <div class="topbar-right">
    <nav class="topbar-nav">
      <a href="/" class="topbar-link">SCORES</a>
      <a href="/support" class="topbar-link topbar-link--active topbar-link--support" aria-current="page">
        <svg class="support-heart" width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/></svg>
        <span class="support-label">SUPPORT</span>
      </a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</div>

<main>

  <!-- ── 1. HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-wordmark">HGB</div>
      <h1 class="hero-headline">HockeyGameBot runs so you don't have to.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">32 team bots. Live scores. Playoff cards. Twitch stream. iOS app.<br>All automated, all season.</p>
      <a href="https://ko-fi.com/hockeygamebot" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink:0"><path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/></svg>
        Support HockeyGameBot
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 2. WHAT IS THIS ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 class="section-title">What is HockeyGameBot?</h2>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>HockeyGameBot is a side project I've been building since 2019. It's a network of 32 team-specific bots — one for every NHL franchise — that automatically track live games and post play-by-play updates to X (Twitter), Bluesky, and Threads. Goals, penalties, period ends, three stars, final scores. All of it, automatically, every night.</p>
        <p>Over 8,000 followers across 32 accounts, and growing. On busy nights with 14+ games, every bot is firing simultaneously, each one tracking its own team's game independently. There's also a live Twitch scoreboard showing every game at once, an iOS app with push notifications and win probability charts, and playoff bracket cards that generate automatically after every series result.</p>
        <p>None of this runs on a big team or corporate budget. It's one person, one server, and a lot of Python. Everything you see on this site and in those bots was written from scratch.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 3. WHAT IT COSTS TO RUN ─────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 class="section-title">What it costs to run</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">These are the real monthly numbers during the regular season and playoffs.</p>
      <div class="cost-table-wrap">
        <table class="cost-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Service</th>
              <th>Cost</th>
              <th>What it does</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Hetzner VPS (CPX32)</td>
              <td>~$12/mo</td>
              <td>Runs all 32 bots simultaneously during game nights</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>X (Twitter) API</td>
              <td>~$65/mo</td>
              <td>32 accounts × ~$2/mo avg — required to post anything</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Backblaze B2</td>
              <td>~$3–5/mo</td>
              <td>Stores goal GIFs, period charts, playoff cards</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Cloudflare Workers</td>
              <td>~$0</td>
              <td>API layer and live scoreboard backend (free tier)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Domain &amp; DNS</td>
              <td>~$2/mo</td>
              <td>hockeygamebot.com</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="cost-total">
              <td>Total (peak)</td>
              <td>~$85/mo</td>
              <td></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="cost-note">Offseason costs drop significantly. Playoffs cost more. X API fees are by far the biggest line item — posting from 32 accounts adds up fast.</p>
      <p class="cost-note cost-note--accent">Every dollar goes directly to keeping the lights on.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 4. WHAT SUPPORTERS GET ──────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 class="section-title">What supporters get</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">We're being honest: supporter perks are still being built. But here's what's planned.</p>
      <ul class="perks-list">
        <li>
          <span class="perk-arrow">→</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Vote on new features</strong>
            <p>Have a say in what gets built next — new card formats, notification types, stat visualizations.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="perk-arrow">→</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Early access to new cards and tools</strong>
            <p>Get new playoff cards, win probability features, and site tools before they go public.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="perk-arrow">→</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Your name in the supporter credits</strong>
            <p>A permanent mention in the project's acknowledgments.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="perk-arrow">→</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Discord access</strong>
            <p>If and when a Discord launches, supporters get in first.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="perks-footer">We're building this with supporters, not for them.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── 5. CTA FOOTER ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section section--cta">
    <div class="section-inner section-inner--center">
      <h2 class="section-title">Ready to help?</h2>
      <a href="https://ko-fi.com/hockeygamebot" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink:0"><path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/></svg>
        Support on Ko-fi
      </a>
      <p class="cta-alt">
        Not ready to support? Follow a team bot on X or Bluesky — it's free and it helps.<br>
        <a href="https://hockeygamebot.com/bots" class="cta-link">Find your team bot →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <span class="footer-brand">HGB</span>
    <span class="footer-sep">·</span>
    <a href="/" class="footer-link">Scores</a>
    <a href="https://ko-fi.com/hockeygamebot" class="footer-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ko-fi</a>
    <span class="footer-copy">Built with 🏒 by <a href="https://twitter.com/mattdonders" class="footer-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@mattdonders</a></span>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
:root {
  --bg: #090909;
  --card: #111;
  --border: #1c1c1c;
  --border2: #252525;
  --muted: #555;
  --text: #999;
  --text-secondary: #777;
  --white: #f5f5f5;
  --red: #ff3d3d;
  --red-dim: rgba(255, 61, 61, 0.12);
  --red-border: rgba(255, 61, 61, 0.3);
}

html, body {
  background: var(--bg);
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.65;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

/* ── TOP BAR ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.topbar {
  height: 44px;
  background: var(--red);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0 24px;
  gap: 16px;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
}
.brand {
  font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-decoration: none;
}
.brand-sub {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
}
.topbar-right {
  margin-left: auto;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}
.topbar-nav {
  display: flex;
  gap: 6px;
}
.topbar-link {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  border-radius: 3px;
  transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
}
.topbar-link:hover { color: #fff; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
.topbar-link--active { color: #fff; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
.topbar-link--support {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 5px;
}
.support-heart { flex-shrink: 0; opacity: 0.9; }
.support-label { display: inline; }

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .topbar { height: 48px; padding: 0 16px; gap: 10px; }
  .brand-sub { display: none; }
  .support-label { display: none; }
}

/* ── LAYOUT ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.section {
  padding: 80px 24px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.section--alt {
  background: #0c0c0c;
}
.section--cta {
  padding: 100px 24px;
  border-bottom: none;
}
.section-inner {
  max-width: 720px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.section-inner--center {
  text-align: center;
}

/* ── HERO ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero {
  padding: 100px 24px 90px;
  text-align: center;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.hero-inner {
  max-width: 680px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 24px;
}
.hero-wordmark {
  font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
  font-size: 56px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--red);
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  line-height: 1;
}
.hero-headline {
  font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 44px);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--white);
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  line-height: 1.15;
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 17px);
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.7;
  max-width: 520px;
}

/* ── BUTTONS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.btn-primary {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  background: var(--red);
  color: #fff;
  font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.1s;
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  background: #ff5252;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}
.btn-primary:active { transform: translateY(0); }

/* ── SECTION HEADINGS ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.section-title {
  font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--white);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.section-lead {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

/* ── PROSE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.prose {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 18px;
}
.prose p {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: #8a8a8a;
  line-height: 1.75;
}

/* ── COST TABLE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.cost-table-wrap {
  overflow-x: auto;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
}
.cost-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.cost-table th {
  padding: 12px 16px;
  text-align: left;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2);
  background: #0a0a0a;
}
.cost-table td {
  padding: 12px 16px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: #7a7a7a;
  vertical-align: top;
}
.cost-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.cost-table td:first-child { color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; }
.cost-table td:nth-child(2) { color: var(--white); font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; }
.cost-table tr:hover:not(.cost-total) td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }

.cost-total td {
  background: var(--red-dim) !important;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--red-border);
  border-bottom: none;
}
.cost-total td:first-child { color: var(--red); }
.cost-total td:nth-child(2) { color: var(--red); font-size: 16px; }

.cost-note {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.cost-note--accent {
  color: var(--white);
  font-weight: 500;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
  padding-left: 14px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}

/* ── PERKS LIST ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.perks-list {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border2);
  border-radius: 6px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.perks-list li {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 20px 24px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  transition: background 0.15s;
}
.perks-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.perks-list li:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
.perk-arrow {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--red);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}
.perks-list strong {
  display: block;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--white);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}
.perks-list p {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}
.perks-footer {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--white);
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ── CTA SECTION ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.cta-alt {
  margin-top: 28px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  line-height: 1.75;
}
.cta-link {
  color: var(--red);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.cta-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

/* ── FOOTER ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.site-footer {
  background: #050505;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  padding: 28px 24px;
}
.footer-inner {
  max-width: 720px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.footer-brand {
  font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--red);
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
}
.footer-sep { color: var(--border2); }
.footer-link {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.15s;
}
.footer-link:hover { color: var(--white); }
.footer-copy {
  margin-left: auto;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--muted);
}

/* ── MOBILE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .hero { padding: 64px 20px 56px; }
  .hero-wordmark { font-size: 44px; }
  .section { padding: 56px 20px; }
  .section--cta { padding: 72px 20px; }
  .cost-table th:nth-child(3),
  .cost-table td:nth-child(3) { display: none; }
  .perks-list li { padding: 16px 16px; gap: 12px; }
  .footer-copy { margin-left: 0; width: 100%; }
}
</style>
